<p class="p1">The Virgin Islands&nbsp;<span class="s1">does not offer online voter registration. For information on how to register to vote or update your registration, visit the territory's&nbsp;voter registration information webpage:</span>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.vivote.gov/voters/register-vote" target="_blank">https://www.vivote.gov/voters/register-vote</a>.</p>

